00063                 return E_FAIL;

00067         pVal->parray = NULL;
00068         affymetrix_calvin_utilities::AffymetrixGuidTypeList &ids = chp->FileTypeIdentifiers();
00069         int nids = (int)ids.size();
00070         SAFEARRAYBOUND  rgsaBound[1];
00071         rgsaBound[0].lLbound = 0;
00072         rgsaBound[0].cElements = nids;
00073         pVal->parray = SafeArrayCreate(VT_BSTR, 1, rgsaBound);
00074         long index=0;
00075         affymetrix_calvin_utilities::AffymetrixGuidTypeList::iterator it;
00076         for (it=ids.begin(); it!=ids.end(); ++it)
00077         {
00078                 BSTR id = COMStringUtils::ConvertString(*it);

00259 {
00260     affymetrix_calvin_io::MultiDataType dt = (affymetrix_calvin_io::MultiDataType) dataType;
00261     int n = chp->GetNumMetricColumns(dt);
00262     forceIndex = -1;
00263     sigAIndex = -1;
00264     sigBIndex = -1;
00265     for (int i=0; i<n; i++)
00266     {
00267         wstring name = chp->GetMetricColumnName(dt, i);
00268         if (name.find(L"Forced") == 0)
00269         {
00270             forceIndex = i;

00273         else if (sigAIndex == -1)
00274         {
00275             sigAIndex = i;
00276             *signalAName = COMStringUtils::ConvertWString(name);
00277         }
00278         else if (sigBIndex == -1)
00279         {
00280             sigBIndex = i;
00281             *signalBName = COMStringUtils::ConvertWString(name);

00284     return S_OK;

00287 STDMETHODIMP CFusionCHPMultiDataDataCOM::GetGenotypeEntries(MultiDataType dataType, VARIANT* names, VARIANT* calls, VARIANT* confidences, VARIANT* forcedcalls, VARIANT* signalsA, VARIANT* signalsB, int startIndex, int *pVal)
00288 {
00289     affymetrix_calvin_io::MultiDataType dt = (affymetrix_calvin_io::MultiDataType) dataType;
00290     int n = chp->GetEntryCount(dt);
00291     long ubound = 0;
00292     long lbound = 0;
00293     long index;
00294     SafeArrayGetUBound(names->parray, 1, &ubound);
00295     SafeArrayGetLBound(names->parray, 1, &lbound);
00296     int len = ubound - lbound + 1;
00297     int count = (len + startIndex <= n ? len : n - startIndex);
00298     *pVal = count;
00299     float fvalue;
00300     u_int8_t ubvalue;
00301     affymetrix_calvin_data::ProbeSetMultiDataGenotypeData entry;
00302     for (int i=0; i<count; i++)
00303     {
00304         index = (long) i;
00305         chp->GetGenotypeEntry(dt, i+startIndex, entry);
00306 
00307         _bstr_t bstr = entry.name.c_str();
00308         BSTR bsstr = bstr.copy();
00309         SafeArrayPutElement(names->parray, &index, bsstr);
00310         SysFreeString(bsstr);
00311 
00312         SafeArrayPutElement(calls->parray, &index, &entry.call);
00313 
00314         SafeArrayPutElement(confidences->parray, &index, &entry.confidence);
00315 
00316         ubvalue = entry.metrics[forceIndex].GetValueUInt8();
00317         SafeArrayPutElement(forcedcalls->parray, &index, &ubvalue);
00318 
00319         fvalue = entry.metrics[sigAIndex].GetValueFloat();
00320         SafeArrayPutElement(signalsA->parray, &index, &fvalue);
